trans-unit.source: Defines the configuration element for a peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: Define o elemento de configuração para um resolvedor de pares.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the configuration element for this peer resolver if it is a custom peer resolver implementation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o elemento de configuração para esse resolvedor peer se é uma implementação do resolvedor de pares personalizado.

trans-unit.source: This property contains an instance of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement> if the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement.Mode%2A> property is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade contém uma instância de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement>se a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement.Mode%2A>propriedade é definida como <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement.Mode%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement"></xref> that contains the configuration element for the peer resolver if it is a custom peer resolver implementation.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement"></xref>que contém o elemento de configuração para o resolvedor peer se é uma implementação do resolvedor de pares personalizado.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the type of the peer resolver represented by this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém e define o tipo do resolvedor peer representado por este elemento de configuração.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref> enumeration value that specifies the type of peer resolvder represented by this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref>valor de enumeração que especifica o tipo de ponto a ponto resolvder representada por este elemento de configuração.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the referral policy for peer resolvers configured with this element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém e define a política de referência para o resolvedor peer configurado com este elemento.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref> that specifies the referral policy for peer resolvers configured with this element.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref>que especifica a diretiva de referência para o resolvedor peer configurado com este elemento.
